g.text: wants to add a scooter to the available scooter list of one pharmacy
shows the list of scooters registered, but with no pharmacy related
selects the scooter he wants to add
shows the list of pharmacys and asks to choose the one
he wants to add a scooter
inserts the pharmacy id where he wants to add the scooter choosen
adds the scooter choosen to the pharmacy choosen
